
I have created a HFSA-MOM6 based 3DVAR workflow. Please test it at your convenience 
(10 minutes to copy and run).

(1) cd /work2/noaa/hwrf/save/yongzuo

(2) cp -r MOM6_3DVAR (your path)/.

(3) In parm/exp.config, change JOB_ACCT=marine-cpu

(4) In crontab/cronjob_mom6_3dvar.sh, change HOME3DVAR and WORK3DVAR to your paths

(5) cd crontab

(6) ./cronjob_mom6_3dvar.sh

########################################
(a) cd /work2/noaa/hwrf/save/yongzuo
(b) cp -r MOM6_3DVAR_branch (your path)/MOM6_3DVAR
(c) cd MOM6_3DVAR/crontab
(d) In install_link.sh, change HOME3DVAR to your paths 
(e) ./install_link.sh
(f) perform (3) (4) (5) (6)
########################################

